message.content: cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CVPR - The paper deals with visual place recognition for small unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper specifically focuses on the use of local image descriptors for VPR, which involves computer vision techniques (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the trade-off between accuracy and computational effort, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper utilizes standard aerial datasets, which is a common topic in computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CVPR).
